import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'

import EmployeeRegistrationForm from '../myPractice/EmployeeRegistrationForm'
import EmployeeAddPage from '../employee/EmployeeAddPage'
import Signup from "../employee/Signup";
import HomPage from "../employee/HomPage";
import AdminPage from "../employee/AdminPage";
import SalesPage from "../sales/Sales";


const GeneralRouter =()=>{
    return(
        <Router>
            <Switch>
                <Route exact path = "/admin/signup" component = {Signup}/>
                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin" component = {HomPage}/>
                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin/domywork" component = {AdminPage}/>

                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin/employee/add" component = {EmployeeAddPage}/>
                <Route exact path = "/sales/add" component = {SalesPage}/>


                <Route exact path ="/admin/signin/employee/list" component = {EmployeeAddPage}/>



                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin/materials/add" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>
                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin/materials/list" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>
                <Route exact path = "/admin/signin/customers/list" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>

                <Route exact path= "/" component = {HomPage}/>

            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}
export default GeneralRouter
